          <h1 class="article-title">Is High-Stimulation TV Ruining <em>My Child's Focus?</em></h1>
          <div class="article-meta">
            <span>April 29, 2026</span>
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span>8 min read</span>
            <span class="dot"></span>
